Package: sshguard
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, iptables, systemd, python3-numpy, python3-pandas, python3-sklearn, python3-pip
Description: LSTM-based SSH intrusion detection system
 SSHGuard monitors SSH authentication logs using machine learning
 to detect slow-rate brute force attacks that evade traditional
 threshold-based detection systems like fail2ban.
